"By Primus, you want to lose again" Wildrider yelled. He quickly
transformed and followed quickly, but started to swerve severly around the
road trying to catch up. "If you lose again, I get youre cubes" he yelled.


>"Yessa, returning to base." replies Drag Strip. He closes his
>comlink and turns to Speedbreaker, "We've been told to return to
>base," and then with a glint in his eye, "Last one back was born in
>a slag heap!" He then jumps up, transforms in mid air, lands on the
>ground with his tires squeeling as he accelerates of back to base.
